column5: Bump the deployment target to 5.1.1 so that we can support 64-bit builds.
Improve performance when editing brush settings.
Clean up stylus stuff. Currently only supporting Pogo Connect on iPads.
Fix Issue #1: Paintings do not appear on the canvas in Release builds.
Remove reference to nonexistent UITableView subclass.
Support high definition paintings on the new 64-bit iPads.
